"""
PART III Income

15. Income for the purposes of the Act

(5)

(a)

Editorial note: current text valid from 2025-03-21.

For the purposes of section 15(1)(j) (income to include income of prescribed descriptions), income of the following descriptions is prescribed—

a payment made—

(i)

under article 30 of the Naval, Military and Air Forces Etc. (Disablement and Death) Service Pensions Order 2006, in any case where article 30(1)(b) applies; or
"""

payment_is_made_under_service_pensions_order_2006_article_30:
    entity: Person
    period: Day
    dtype: Boolean

service_pensions_order_2006_article_30_1_b_applies_in_that_case:
    entity: Person
    period: Day
    dtype: Boolean

payment_made_under_service_pensions_order_2006_article_30_where_article_30_1_b_applies_15_5_a_i:
